
1.
service A  (method A  调用 method B)

#Propagation.REQUIRED
method A {
  method B

  update(entityA);
}

service B

#Propagation.REQUIRED_NEW 或 Propagation.REQUIRED
method B {

  try{
      save(entityB);
  }catch(Exception e){

  }
}


method B #save 抛异常，不影响 method A 的 update 方法。

2

propagation = Propagation.REQUIRED_NEW,rollbackFor = Exception.class
method B throws Exception{
  save(entityB);
}